       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. SUBTRACT-FROM.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-BALANCE  PIC 9(5) VALUE 1000.
       01 WS-WITHDRAW PIC 9(4) VALUE 250.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "Before:   " WS-BALANCE
           SUBTRACT WS-WITHDRAW FROM WS-BALANCE
           DISPLAY "After:    " WS-BALANCE
           SUBTRACT 100 FROM WS-BALANCE
           DISPLAY "Final:    " WS-BALANCE
           STOP RUN.
